        "subject": "LU-12827 ldiskfs: fix ldiskfs_xattr_inode_iget error checking",
        "message": "LU-12827 ldiskfs: fix ldiskfs_xattr_inode_iget error checking\n\nIn ldiskfs_xattr_inode_iget, ldiskfs_iget could return an\nerror value and calling is_bad_inode on it will crash the server.\n\nThe problem has already been addressed in upstream by\nbab79b04999c ext4: change ext4_xattr_inode_iget() signature,\nmerge the commit to our ext4-large-eas.patch.\n\nLinux-commit: bab79b04999ccbbf59f1693d0783cd6ae27e4278\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Dongyang <dongyangli@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ia048687b3754a7580fa971c18b996ddb36d9a34c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
